&lt;/div>
&lt;/td>
 &lt;td style="text-align: left">Gyofu&lt;/td>
 &lt;td style="text-align: left">Single target combo starter. 240 potency. +5 Kenki.&lt;/td>
 &lt;/tr>
 &lt;tr>
 &lt;td style="text-align: left">
&lt;div class="md__image">
 &lt;img id="[312 438 367 361 146 330]" src="https://xivapi.com/i/003000/003152_hr1.png" onclick="openModal(this.id)" alt="Jinpu" />
&lt;/div>
&lt;/td>
 &lt;td style="text-align: left">Jinpu&lt;/td>
 &lt;td style="text-align: left">Single target second step combo. 140 potency, 300 potency if combo from Hakaze. Combo Bonus: Fugetsu buff (increased damage dealt by 13% for 40s), +5 Kenki.&lt;/td>
 &lt;/tr>
 &lt;tr>
 &lt;td style="text-align: left">
&lt;div class="md__image">
 &lt;img id="[340 105 295 279 398 428]" src="https://xivapi.com/i/003000/003156_hr1.png" onclick="openModal(this.id)" alt="Shifu" />
&lt;/div>
&lt;/td>
 &lt;td style="text-align: left">Shifu&lt;/td>
 &lt;td style="text-align: left">Single target second step combo. 140 potency, 300 potency if combo from Hakaze. Combo Bonus: Fuka buff (reduces GCD and autoattack delay by 13%) for 40s, +5 Kenki.&lt;/td>
 &lt;/tr>
 &lt;tr>
 &lt;td style="text-align: left">
&lt;div class="md__image">
